<h3>How to book your Reindeer ride in Lapland</h3>
<p><span>You can add excursions to your holiday package via your '<a href="https://my.inghams.co.uk/login">My Booking</a>' portal or you can speak to a member of our UK based team on <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111.</span></span></p>
<p><strong>Please note:</strong> Times and distances are approximate and may vary due to weather conditions. Reindeer Safari child age 4-12yrs. <span>Children younger than 4 are not allowed to take part, but can be pre-booked onto the transfer to spectate (must be accompanied by an adult at all times).</span></p>
